extends /includes/base
block content
  section#hero
    .hero-layer.paralax(style='background-image: url(/static/img/hero.vip.jpg)' data-component='BgImage' data-props={field:'hero', defaultURL:'/static/img/hero.vip.jpg'})
    .hero-layer.hero-layer-text.penguin-bg-image-sibling
      .hero-layer-text-v.active
        .wrapper3
          h1.bg-title.penguin-sp
            span.light-blue(data-component='MediumEditor' data-props={field:'title'}) VIP Weekly
    span#hero-arrow
  .wrapper3.pt-120.pb-90
    .hello.hello-inner(data-component='MediumEditor' data-props={field:'desc'})
      | VIP Weekly are cycles of lessons for high school students on Values – Improvisation – Presentation.
  .wrapper4
    p(data-component='MediumEditor' data-props={field:'cont'})
      | For each VIP cycle, we start with V-Class on values such as love, forgiveness, positive attitude, etc. Students are encouraged to write stories from their own experience based on the value discussed in class. Then the I-Class is designed to improve communication and building confidence through improvisation. The final lesson P-Class is dedicated to student presentations and discussions. Students are encouraged to present their stories on the topic from the V-Class.
    //- br
    //- a.btn.btn-alt(data-component='Link' data-props={href:'/resources'}) Resources
  .square-images.pt-90
    div(style='background-image: url(/static/img/sq1.jpg)')
    div(style='background-image: url(/static/img/sq2.jpg)')
    div(style='background-image: url(/static/img/sq3.jpg)')
  section.stories.pt-120
    h3.text-center(data-component='Inplace' data-props={field:'title_2'}) STORIES
    .isotope
      .isotope-content.bg-grey(data-component="StoryList" data-props={filter:"vip weekly"})
    .text-center.bg-grey.btn-more
      a.btn.btn-alt(data-component='Link' data-props={href:'/stories'}) Read All Stories
